OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FColombia's last active     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fguerrilla group agrees     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Ftruce                      
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Colombia's government and the country's
OL,6, last active rebel group have agreed a  
OL,7, truce - their latest step towards peace
OL,8, after almost 60 years of conflict.     
OL,10,FThe National Liberation Army (ELN) said
OL,11,Fit would stop fighting from Thursday,  
OL,12,Fahead of a full ceasefire in August.   
OL,14,FColombia's defence minister confirmed  
OL,15,Fthe armed forces would also be told to 
OL,16,Fhalt offensives from that time.        
OL,18,FHowever, the ELN said it would defend  
OL,19,Fitself from any attacks by the military
OL,20,For other armed groups.                 
